  "text": "Although at least one other secondary structure makes use of SOAP for inter-process communication (e.g. PROS-PECT-PSPP [CITATION_1] ), the interface is not made public nor is a WSDL interface definition provided. To our knowledge, this is the first publicly available SOAP interface for a protein secondary structure prediction method.",
